              "content": "=Write a reply to this {{$json.platform}} review.\n\nReviewer: {{$json.reviewerName}}\nStar Rating: {{$json.starRatingNumeric}} out of 5\nReview: \"{{$json.reviewText}}\"\n\nRemember: If rating < 3, apply the Reputation Shield Protocol."
